title: The New Slaves
description:
Rare, VERY hard to find industrial rock album that has been licensed to some films and TV shows.  Definitely a hidden gem, been listening to it solidly for years now.

I bought this from the band themselves after a show in Cleveland back in 2004.  It was a pre-release copy that got caught up in a legal battle and eventually ended up on Klayton (Celldweller)'s FiXT indie label in 2008.

I think more people should check out this band.

Remember, support independent music to keep the artists alive!
